<tr><td nowrap width="20%" valign=baseline align=right><b>Notable Features: </b></td><td colspan=4 align=left valign=baseline>Instead of <a target="glossary" class="glossarylink" href="/glossary.php#Flipper">flippers</a>, there is one movable <a target="glossary" class="glossarylink" href="/glossary.php#Bumper">bumper</a> acting as a bat and controlled by buttons on each side of the <a target="glossary" class="glossarylink" href="/glossary.php#Cabinet">cabinet</a>. <a target="glossary" class="glossarylink" href="/glossary.php#Playfield">Playfield</a> <a target="glossary" class="glossarylink" href="/glossary.php#Animation">animation</a> is a rotating disk that moves white baseballs around the bases and back home.</td></tr>
